{"tid":495900,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底人生會唔會去到一個位轉運？","createTime":"2017-12-11T07:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T04:14:55.000Z","uid":45028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a6ccd1259bff350f4818a15e643ffefedd3e7d","tid":495900,"uid":45028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:29:21.000Z","msg":"做左廿年人，一直以黎嘅生活上都無咩好彩嘅出現。抽咩都唔中，買咩都唔升，賭咩都唔贏。<br />\n但身邊有啲朋友真係可以一世人好好彩好好命。<br />\n到底人生會唔會有個位會轉運 定好迷信咁要靠積德？"},{"pid":"36dbe7ee5653d535c117c834b7bca6e4e79bd29a","tid":495900,"uid":34286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T07:43:41.000Z","msg":"行運太早無用"},{"pid":"2cf2b0679eaf390a983175c964ea2d6406605272","tid":495900,"uid":4384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0492d3d7ec5c8b8e808caa2fe1e3329769863b8e","tid":495900,"uid":45028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行運太早無用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都會問自己係咪唔知足<br />\n但真係成世人都無運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但世上嘅野始終都好多係講運"},{"pid":"7531bdca00a14027d1e3dd8daf05388c3336529e","tid":495900,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"我都好撚黑 曾經諗過課金買啲開光催運法器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8592ea3d8f4dd3bb744b294dad41036ee76b7abc","tid":495900,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"有啲人係會黑足一世"},{"pid":"697d684ad034204a316650e7424b64b0154cac49","tid":495900,"uid":45028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T18:24:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲人係會黑足一世</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c621749111b66f8c2ca31741e7d95824e9a71384","tid":495900,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T18:27:07.000Z","msg":"出生係窮閪家庭俾你幾好運都冇用<br />\n童年過得差<br />\n出黎做野仲要俾家用"},{"pid":"7a700f1516f9d5984b065161150794dc1e529506","tid":495900,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T18:28:42.000Z","msg":"信埋呢d on9野<br />\n幫我含撚轉運啦"},{"pid":"4156fe6175f829cd345000b22df77c923ed426ae","tid":495900,"uid":2429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T18:32:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.dailyenglishquote.com/2015/11/thomas-jefferson-6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailyenglishquote.com%2F2015%2F11%2Fthomas-jefferson-6%2F&d=OZLboJ8a3aGlrRIfUsiPBEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b9d8bb87\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailyenglishquote.com/2015/11/thomas-jefferson-6/</a><br />\n<br />\n「If you want something you've never had, you must be willing to do something you've never done.」<br />\n&mdash; Thomas Jefferson, The Third U.S. President<br />\n<br />\n「若想得到你從未擁有的東西，你得願意做你從未做過的事。」&ndash; 湯瑪斯‧傑佛遜 (美國第三任總統)<br />\n<br />\n    湯瑪斯‧傑佛遜 (1743-1826) 是美國第三任總統，也是美國「獨立宣言」的主要起草人，為美國開國元勛之一，傑佛遜博學多聞，是政治家、建築師、考古學家、音樂家、發明家等。"},{"pid":"c63d4e0a071950d131cc7df5247368f62ac39c47","tid":495900,"uid":34286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T00:26:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出生係窮閪家庭俾你幾好運都冇用<br />\n童年過得差<br />\n出黎做野仲要俾家用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大把人三四十歲先發圍啦"},{"pid":"75c05cc8bd03fa4c2a41dee93efe7187a311be6d","tid":495900,"uid":22557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T00:45:47.000Z","msg":"朋友去算命<br />\n睇相佬話佢三十歲前運氣好差有啲坎坷，所以三十歲前既朋友係真正既朋友，無離棄佢咁話<br />\n朋友：咁三十歲後係咪會轉運呀？<br />\n睇相：er<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫無咁難過咁啦 都算唔得上好運"},{"pid":"8ec52db10bb2781d4f2c697464a36791454baf96","tid":495900,"uid":19776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T00:47:31.000Z","msg":"人唔一定愈黎愈好，可以愈黎愈差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b791a1c7c0fb5c16c895f83f9ebc813230118b","tid":495900,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T04:14:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友去算命<br />\n睇相佬話佢三十歲前運氣好差有啲坎坷，所以三十歲前既朋友係真正既朋友，無離棄佢咁話<br />\n朋友：咁三十歲後係咪會轉運呀？<br />\n睇相：er<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫無咁難過咁啦 都算唔得上好運</blockquote><br />\nCertified <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}